headline: Microsoft and Meta earnings, April PCE: What to Watch
summary: Julie Hyman and Josh Lipton preview the biggest market stories and economic data to come out on Wednesday, April 30, including the latest earnings results from Microsoft (MSFT), Meta Platforms (META), Qualcomm (QCOM), Robinhood Markets (HOOD), and Stellantis (STLA), as well as April's Personal Consumption Expenditures (PCE) index. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
